API/DOMParser\"><code>DOMParser</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/DOMPoint\"><code>DOMPoint</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/DOMPointReadOnly\"><code>DOMPointReadOnly</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/DOMRect\"><code>DOMRect</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/DOMTimeStamp\"><code>DOMTimeStamp</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/DOMTokenList\"><code>DOMTokenList</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/DocumentFragment\"><code>DocumentFragment</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/DocumentType\"><code>DocumentType</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/Element\"><code>Element</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/Event\"><code>Event</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/EventTarget\"><code>EventTarget</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/HTMLCollection\"><code>HTMLCollection</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/MutationObserver\"><code>MutationObserver</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/NamedNodeMap\"><code>NamedNodeMap</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/Node\"><code>Node</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/NodeIterator\"><code>NodeIterator</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/NodeList\"><code>NodeList</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/ProcessingInstruction\"><code>ProcessingInstruction</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Range\"><code>Range</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/StaticRange\"><code>StaticRange</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Text\"><code>Text</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/TextDecoder\"><code>TextDecoder</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/TextEncoder\"><code>TextEncoder</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/TimeRanges\"><code>TimeRanges</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/TreeWalker\"><code>TreeWalker</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/XMLDocument\"><code>XMLDocument</code></a></li></ol></details></li></ol>","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<div id=\"sect1\">\n<div id=\"sect2\"></div>\n</div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"summary","title":"Sumário","isH3":false,"content":"<p>Retorna o primeiro elemento dentro do documento (usando ordenação em profundidade, pré-ordenada e transversal dos nós do documento) que corresponde ao grupo especificado de seletores.</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"syntax","title":"Sintaxe<span class=\"st\"> </span>","isH3":false,"content":"<pre class=\"notranslate\"><em>element</em> = document.querySelector(<em>selectors</em>);</pre>\n\n<p>Onde:</p>\n\n<ul>\n <li><code>element</code> é um objeto <a class=\"page-not-created\" title=\"A documentação sobre isto ainda não foi escrita; por favor considere contribuir!\"><code>Element</code></a>.</li>\n <li><code>selectors</code> é uma string que contém um ou mais seletores CSS separados por vírgulas.</li>\n</ul>","titleAsText":"Sintaxe "}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"example","title":"Exemplo","isH3":false,"content":"<p>Neste exemplo, o primeiro elemento no documento com a classe \"<code>myclass</code>\" é retornado:</p>\n\n<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: js notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token keyword\">var</span> el <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> document<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">querySelector</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">\".myclass\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n</code></pre></div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"notes","title":"Notas","isH3":false,"content":"<p>Retorna <code>null</code> se nenhum resultado for encontrado; caso contrário, retorna o primeiro elemento correspondente.</p>\n\n<p>Se o seletor utilizado for um <code>ID</code> e este <code>ID</code> foi erroneamente utilizado várias vezes no documento, ele retorna somente o primeiro elemento correspondente.</p>\n\n<p>Gera uma exceção <code>SYNTAX_ERR</code> se o grupo de seletores utilizado for inválido.</p>\n\n<p><code>querySelector()</code> foi introduzido com a API de seletores.</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"browser_compatibility","title":"Compatibilidade dos navegadores","isH3":false,"content":"<p></p><div class=\"notecard note\" id=\"sect3\"><strong><a href=\"https://github.com/mdn/browser-compat-data\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">Estamos convertendo nossos dados de compatibilidade para o formato JSON</a></strong>.\n            Esta tabela de compatibilidade ainda usa o formato antigo,\n            pois ainda não convertemos os dados que ela contém.\n            <strong><a href=\"/en-US/docs/MDN/Structures/Compatibility_tables\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">Descubra como você pode ajudar! (en-US)</a></strong></div>\n\n<div class=\"htab\" id=\"sect4\">\n    <a id=\"AutoCompatibilityTable\" name=\"AutoCompatibilityTable\"></a>\n    <ul>\n        <li class=\"selected\"><a href=\"#compat-desktop\">Desktop</a></li>\n        <li><a href=\"#compat-mobile\">Dispositivo móvel</a></li>\n    </ul>\n</div><p></p>\n\n<div id=\"compat-desktop\">\n<table class=\"compat-table\">\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <th>Feature</th>\n   <th>Chrome</th>\n   <th>Firefox (Gecko)</th>\n   <th>Internet Explorer</th>\n   <th>Opera</th>\n   <th>Safari (WebKit)</th>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td>Basic support</td>\n   <td>1</td>\n   <td>3.5 (1.9.1)<br>\n    <a href=\"https://bugzilla.mozilla.org/show_bug.cgi?id=416317\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">bug&nbsp;416317</a></td>\n   <td>8</td>\n   <td>10</td>\n   <td>3.2 (525.3)<br>\n    <a rel=\"external noopener\" href=\"https://bugs.webkit.org/show_bug.cgi?id=16587\" class=\"external\" title=\"\">WebKit bug 16587</a></td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>\n</div>\n\n<div id=\"compat-mobile\">\n<table class=\"compat-table\">\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <th>Feature</th>\n   <th>Android</th>\n   <th>Firefox Mobile (Gecko)</th>\n   <th>IE Mobile</th>\n   <th>Opera Mobile</th>\n   <th>Safari Mobile</th>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td>Basic support</td>\n   <td>2.1</td>\n   <td>yes</td>\n   <td>9</td>\n   <td>10.0</td>\n   <td>3.2</td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>\n</div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"specification","title":"Especificação","isH3":false,"content":"<ul>\n <li><a class=\"external\" href=\"https://www.w3.org/TR/selectors-api/\" rel=\" noopener\">Selectors API</a></li>\n</ul>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"see_also","title":"Veja também:","isH3":false,"content":"<ul>\n <li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/Document/querySelectorAll\"><code>document.querySelectorAll()</code></a></li>\n <li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/Element/querySelector\"><code>element.querySelector()</code></a></li>\n <li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/Element/querySelectorAll\"><code>element.querySelectorAll()</code></a></li>\n <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Code_snippets/QuerySelector\" title=\"This is a link to an unwritten page\" class=\"page-not-created\">Code snippets for querySelector</a></li>\n</ul>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"Sumário","id":"summary"},{"text":"Sintaxe<span class=\"st\"> </span>","id":"syntax"},{"text":"Exemplo","id":"example"},{"text":"Notas","id":"notes"},{"text":"Compatibilidade dos navegadores","id":"browser_compatibility"},{"text":"Especificação","id":"specification"},{"text":"Veja também:","id":"see_also"}],"summary":"Retorna o primeiro elemento dentro do documento (usando ordenação em profundidade, pré-ordenada e transversal dos nós do documento) que corresponde ao grupo especificado de seletores.","popularity":0.0046,"modified":"2022-07-19T02:29:32.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"Document.querySelector()","locale":"de","native":"Deutsch"},{"title":"Document.querySelector()","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"Document.querySelector()","locale":"es","native":"Español"},{"title":"document.querySelector","locale":"fr","native":"Français"},{"title":"Document.querySelector()","locale":"ja","native":"日本語"},{"title":"Document.querySelector()","locale":"ko","native":"한국어"},{"title":"Document.querySelector()","locale":"pl","native":"Polski"},{"title":"Document.querySelector()","locale":"ru","native":"Русский"},{"title":"document.querySelector()","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)"},{"title":"document.querySelector","locale":"zh-TW","native":"正體中文 (繁體)"}],"source":